Deployed on Heroku App :- https://still-forest-14101.herokuapp.com/ you can access the same 
Used Tools:- MongoDB,ExpressJS,NodeJS 

Steps:
Publish your Code to Github and Connect to Heroku:-
1. git push heroku master
2. heroku ps:scale web=1 --> For Starting an Instance on server
3. heroku open

Important Points:
Do Change the Main File to your target js File for Starting the Web

"scripts": {
    "start": "node index.js",
    "dev":"nodemon index.js"
  }


